
as of 6 february 2006:

- cursor positioning with mouse

- word wrap

- grab from a console or run a shell inside

- scrolling

- colors

- fancy edit modes, justify functions

- integrate with mail clients (let's start with mutt)

- playback control (rewind, fast forward etc.)

- daemon mode, timed pipe input/output from sockets

- protocol compression



this project just started, u'r welcome to help!

send remarks and patches to http://dyne.org/hackers_contact.php

or get in touch with coders via irc.freenode.net channel #dyne

